        <!-- 2. WIDGETS EXPLAINING COLUMNS -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-24">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded border border-gray-200" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="50">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-3">
                    <div class="bg-white p-2 rounded shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                        <i data-lucide="calculator" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Interactive Calculators</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Lead-gen tools embedded in the UI allowing clients to self-estimate costs for Free Zone/Mainland setups. This replaces static "Contact Us for Pricing" tactics.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded border border-gray-200" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-3">
                    <div class="bg-white p-2 rounded shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                        <i data-lucide="lock" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Customer Portals</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Dedicated login dashboards for tracking application status, uploading documents, and paying invoices securely, marking the transition from Agency to SaaS.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded border border-gray-200" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="150">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-3">
                    <div class="bg-white p-2 rounded shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                        <i data-lucide="languages" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Multi-language Support</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    True bilingual architecture (not auto-translate plugins) targeting Native Arabic SEO and layout mirroring (RTL). Shuraa relies heavily on this, bridging international and local investors natively.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded border border-gray-200" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-3">
                    <div class="bg-white p-2 rounded shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                        <i data-lucide="bot" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">AI Chatbots / Tools</h4>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Pre-trained AI models built directly into the site (not basic live human chat) capable of answering complex jurisdiction and visa rule questions instantly 24/7.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3. RECOMMENDED SITES TO VISIT -->
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold mb-8 tracking-tight pl-2 border-b border-pistos-border pb-4">Recommended Sites to Visit</h2>
            
