                        <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-3 h-3"></i><span>arnifi.com</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 pl-0 md:pl-6 relative">
                    <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 p-2 opacity-5">
                        <i data-lucide="server" class="w-24 h-24 text-gray-900"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3 text-lg">Why Visit: Interactive Elements & SaaS Ecosystem</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Arnifi is currently the most technologically advanced platform in the market. They don't just sell services; they provide a comprehensive dashboard ecosystem with deeply integrated AI and multiple cost calculators.
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-3 rounded border border-yellow-200 text-xs text-yellow-800">
                        <strong>Must see:</strong> Explore their interactive client portals and deep automated integrations to understand the bar Pistos must surpass.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Benchmark 2: A&A Associates -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 bg-white border border-pistos-border p-6 rounded shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group" data-aos="fade-up">
