                    <a href="https://aaconsultancy.ae" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm flex items-center space-x-1 text-pistos-muted hover:text-pistos-black mt-2 font-mono transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-3 h-3"></i><span>aaconsultancy.ae</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 pl-0 md:pl-6 relative">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-2 opacity-5">
                        <i data-lucide="calculator" class="w-24 h-24 text-pistos-black"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-pistos-black mb-3 text-lg">Value Prop: Interactive Lead Generation</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-pistos-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        A&A demonstrates high technological competence. Instead of relying on static text, they provide immediate utility. They have built separate subdomains for an advanced Cost Calculator (<code>calc.aaconsultancy.ae</code>) and a Trade Name Checker (<code>tnc.aaconsultancy.ae</code>).
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-pistos-surface p-3 rounded border border-pistos-border text-xs text-pistos-black">
                        <strong>Market Reality:</strong> They capture client interest by offering free, high-value tools before the client even speaks to an advisor.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

